PrecisAuthority (a) for the leasing to BOMBARDIER INC., for a term of forty-nine (49) years, of some 386,680 square metres of land situate on the grounds of MONTREAL INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT at Dorval, Quebec, which are to be used as the site for its new corporate complex (manufacturing and offices), and (b) to accept the surrender of its current lease (No. 109060).
